io.straas.android.sdk.media.notification

Annotation Type NotificationOptions.NOTIFICATION_ACTIONS


  • @Retention(value=CLASS)
public static @interface NotificationOptions.NOTIFICATION_ACTIONS
    This indicates the actions that can be used in NotificationOptions.Builder.setActions(List, int[]).

    The action could be one of following value:

    • NotificationOptions.ACTION_TOGGLE_PLAYBACK
    • NotificationOptions.ACTION_PREV
    • NotificationOptions.ACTION_NEXT
    • NotificationOptions.ACTION_CLEAR
